casebody.data:
The Children’s House, Appellant, v. Celebrezze, Atty. Gen., Appellee.

[Cite as The Children’s House v. Celebrezze (1992), 63 Ohio St.3d 1206.]

(No. 91-697 Submitted February 12, 1992 Decided March 25, 1992.) John K. Everett, for appellant. Lee I. Fisher, Attorney General, and Monica A. Moloney, for appellee.

The appeal is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently allowed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
